<view class="container data-v-fc85deb8"><view class="header data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="title data-v-fc85deb8">🔧 命名冲突修复验证</text><text class="subtitle data-v-fc85deb8">专门解决Getter/Action命名冲突问题</text></view><view class="problem-section data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="section-title data-v-fc85deb8">🚨 发现的问题</text><view class="problem-card data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="problem-title data-v-fc85deb8">getUserInfo 命名冲突</text><text class="problem-desc data-v-fc85deb8">在User Store中同时存在：</text><text class="code-line data-v-fc85deb8">• Getter: getUserInfo: (state) =&gt; state.userInfo</text><text class="code-line data-v-fc85deb8">• Action: async getUserInfo() { ... }</text><text class="problem-result data-v-fc85deb8">结果：Action被Getter覆盖，导致 "is not a function" 错误</text></view></view><view class="solution-section data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="section-title data-v-fc85deb8">✅ 修复方案</text><view class="solution-card data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="solution-title data-v-fc85deb8">重命名Getter避免冲突</text><text class="code-line data-v-fc85deb8">• 原Getter: getUserInfo → userInfoGetter</text><text class="code-line data-v-fc85deb8">• Action保持: getUserInfo (不变)</text><text class="code-line data-v-fc85deb8">• 更新引用: 所有使用getter的地方</text></view></view><view class="test-section data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="section-title data-v-fc85deb8">🧪 修复验证</text><button class="test-btn primary data-v-fc85deb8" bindtap="{{a}}" disabled="{{b}}"> 验证命名冲突修复 </button><button class="test-btn info data-v-fc85deb8" bindtap="{{c}}" disabled="{{d}}"> 检查User Store结构 </button><button class="test-btn success data-v-fc85deb8" bindtap="{{e}}" disabled="{{f}}"> 验证Getter/Action分离 </button></view><view class="results-section data-v-fc85deb8"><text class="section-title data-v-fc85deb8">📊 测试结果</text><view class="log-container data-v-fc85deb8"><view wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="log" wx:key="c" class="{{['data-v-fc85deb8', 'log-item', log.d]}}"><text class="log-text data-v-fc85deb8">{{log.a}}</text><text class="log-time data-v-fc85deb8">{{log.b}}</text></view></view></view></view>